        simp [h]
        <;> omega 
```

Case 2: `x ≠ a`.
Then left side is `count x (smaller a l) + count x (larger a l)`.
The right side is `count x (smaller a l) + 0 + count x (larger a l)`.
These are equal.

```tactics
